{
  "stem": "2713.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were able to cut the wires, at this time, and to go through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a forest, middle of the night, and nearly everyone ran out from the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What year was this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '44.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was when the Russians-- when the Russians made their first offensive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is what I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what happened when we went into the forest?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shootings were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started to shoot every one of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not the partisans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They knew that the camp is very rich from the Poles that they were our masters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew that everyone has got plenty of money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were from the AK, they used to call themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were those right wing-- what do you call them?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, that was their name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "AK, they used to call themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were killing people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So what did we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We ran back in to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we knew, in the morning, most probably, they will take us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no-- and-- and we were lucky to be able to find our way back into the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the morning, the man, who was our master, the German from the camp, he came along.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, look, I know what happened last night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're a free people now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can do what you want.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am not going to fix the-- the wires.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you want to run away, you can run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you want to live, all you have to do is to dismantle all the machines and everything in the camp, and you'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he didn't fix the fence, didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
